title: Arkivickie
creator: Loren Angela Hernandez
description: Owned by Marivic “Vickie” dela Rosa, Arkivickie is famous for their dish, Siomai Egg (Siomai with Quail Egg). It was established in 2006 and is open from 7:00 AM to 6:00 PM.

title: Minda's Store
creator: Loren Angela Hernandez
description: Minda’s Store is located in front of UP Integrated School. They are known for their fried tusok-tusok and specialty sauce. It was there since 2008 but has been under new ownership since 2018. They are open Monday to Saturday, 7:30 AM to 7:00 PM. They want to say thanks to all their patrons, especially students of UPIS, who buy food every dismissal time. Her message to her regular customers is this: "Salamat sa lahat ng bumibili sa amin. Ingat palagi."
location: University of the Philippines Integrated School

title: Myrna's Store
creator: Loren Angela Hernandez
description: Myrna’s Store is iMath’s one and only kiosk. It was established in 2006 under Samahan ng Manininda sa UPD. Since then, their Combo Meals has been a part of the UP Culture. They are open daily from 7am - 7pm but expect a lot of customers every 10am, 11am, 2pm, and 3pm. They are always thankful to their customers for the support and for treating all their staff with respect.
location: University of the Philippines Diliman College of Science
